srd52:Barbarian a rpg:RuleSetClass ; schema:name "Barbarian"@en ; rpg:classDefinedInRuleSet srd52:SRD52 ; srd52:grantsSavingThrowProficiency srd52:StrengthSave, srd52:ConstitutionSave .
