srd52:AbilityCheckRoll schema:description "Use this roll definition for raw ability checks and skill checks. Skill application is represented by selecting a Skill capability that defaults to an ability and optionally adds proficiency."@en .

srd52:AttackRollDef schema:description "Use this roll definition for weapon attacks, unarmed strikes, and spell attacks; specific features or weapon properties may override the default ability."@en .

